creator: Sara Teasdale
description:
LibriVox recording of The Old Maid by Sara Teasdale.
Read in English by Claudia Salto; Kalif Storch; David Lawrence; Diana Majlinger; debolee; Jannie Meisberger; Julia Niedermaier; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; Pam Castille
LibriVox volunteers bring you 10 recordings of The Old Maid by Sara Teasdale. This was the Weekly Poetry project for September 8, 2013.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (5MB)
